## üéÅ BENEFITS OF SUBMODULE APPROACH

# ‚úÖ Self-contained - rules included in project
# ‚úÖ Version-controlled - lock to specific rules version
# ‚úÖ No machine setup - works immediately after git clone
# ‚úÖ Team-friendly - everyone gets same rules
# ‚úÖ Portable - works on any machine
# ‚úÖ Deterministic - same output everywhere

